Read on Substack&hellip;

Books: &lsquo;Blood Curse&rsquo; by Maurizio de Giovanni I just finished reading Blood Curse: The Springtime of Commissario Ricciardi by Maurizio de Giovanni.
This is the second book in the Commissario Ricciardi mystery series, set in Naples in the 1930s. The series was written and initially published in Italian, but I read the English translation by Antony Shugaar.
