Books: &lsquo;The Siege&rsquo; by Ben Macintyre I just finished reading The Siege: A Six-Day Hostage Crisis and the Daring Special-Forces Operation That Shocked the World by Ben Macintyre.
In 1980, Iranian rebels attacked the Iranian embassy in London, taking more than two dozen hostages and threatening to kill them all if police attempted to enter&hellip;
